{"tid":802208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那人醜唔醜]日籍教授冀港人多賞析粵語文化","createTime":"2018-09-01T09:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T01:43:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5c23da6ec7ec1970722c7a2feae8109cf2b0b7","tid":802208,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318769&d=q6KOYGt1kL0Myl74aCbbNvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=d70e854f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318769&h=eb899220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318769</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有人形容，廣東話是漢語的活化石，當中不少發音和用字，都保留了中古漢語的特色。絕大部分土生土長的香港人，都以廣東話為母語，不過，在「兩文三語」大趨勢下，有人擔心廣東話被矮化，甚至被淘汰，旋即引起坊間一股撐粵語風潮。究竟廣東話在香港面臨的危機有多大？想撐粵語又應該如何做？今集《經緯線》會同大家打爛沙盆問到篤。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這班教育大學的學生都是來自內地，他們來香港讀書之前，一句廣東話都不懂。教他們說廣東話的老師都不是香港人，他是來自日本的片岡新教授。暑假期間，他為一班內地生補補習。</strong><br />\n<br />\n片岡新大學主修中文，畢業後輾轉從日本來到香港的大學工作。當時他第一次接觸廣東話便「一見鍾情」，到2004年，他決定修讀關於廣東話的碩士課程。<br />\n<br />\n片岡新現在已成為本港研究粵語的權威之一，主力鑽研由十九世紀至今廣東話發音和用字的演變。不過除了研究廣東話文法，片岡新更欣賞廣東話文化。<br />\n<br />\n星期日晚播出的經緯線，還會帶大家看看坊間不同人士怎樣各出其謀撐粵語。"},{"pid":"3e482fc1c58768e5b7cedea3aa6c3b68cd87eaa5","tid":802208,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4171474e8a6aa2916f899a2aaf65616982d51495","tid":802208,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"外國人比起香港班狗官更識珍惜廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b97f66b9e452ffa17c8e41e83c4fa45f592066d","tid":802208,"uid":153689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:58:08.000Z","msg":"香港班狗官表示大家識蝗語就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6762295e4d646c15f7ae8019aae9893a2a0a0872","tid":802208,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"犀利"},{"pid":"eb52839ff616bfe342e0541931ffa5d797b490d3","tid":802208,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"我耐你老母they"},{"pid":"e65f91290656e316388ca18a68b87ef1a1e2b61c","tid":802208,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等睇反日撚衝出黎話日本仔偽虛假惺惺"},{"pid":"a3abc56c796e11f3660c34dc2d11b6c624c42482","tid":802208,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a112623e1033f492044216f2369c133d8f919b6b","tid":802208,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:43:26.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}